Trading, distribution and services group Bidvest said on Monday it had approved the appointment of Mark Steyn as CFO and executive director from March 1, replacing Peter Meijer who is retiring.
The company also said its trading profit grew 12 percent to R3.1 billion in the half year to December 2017, while its headline earnings per share rose 12.5 percent to 574 cents per share.
